rComments: Professor Foote is GREAT! The books were easy and interesting. Everything you need for the class is in the lectures. The two tests are easy enough. Go to lectures, they are funny. And NO ESSAYS!

Prof. Foote was awesome! Her lectures were really interesting, even if she talked too fast sometimes. Anything you needed for the in class writings she told you about in class, and the midterm and final were easy! If you have her tell her how awesome she is!
VERY VERY easy class.  you get to read some good books, and most of them are on the net or (spark/classic)notes.com
Foote was awesome! Also the semester I took it we read tons of science fiction. A very pleasant voice too.
Awesome professor! Class was easy and entertaining, definitely would recommend!

hilarious, down-to-earth, makes everything understandable, very clear by using relatable ideas.  I had a blast in this class.  She really lets you explore writing nonconventionally and makes you laugh all the time.
